# Prettier ignore — keep `make format` (prettier --write .) and the
# `prettier --check .` gate scoped to hand-authored source only.
#
# These entries mirror the build/coverage paths ignored in the repository
# .gitignore so Prettier never rewrites or flags generated artifacts:
#   dist/      -> Vite build output (tsc -b && vite build)
#   coverage/  -> Vitest/coverage reports
# Without this file Prettier would walk dist/ and report the minified bundles
# as "code style issues", making the format gate noisy and non-idempotent.
dist/
coverage/
